Yoshida no Time Slip Fumai-kou: A Matsue City collaboration anime with Eagle Talon. A young Matsudaira Harusato (aka Matsudaira Fumai) who was once the ruled of Matsue time slips to the present. Yoshida ends up explaining Fumai's achievements to Fumai himself.

['Heisei Matsue Kaidan: Ayashi', 'Matsue Kankou Taishi Sanri ga Iku! Matsue Ghost Tour', 'Yoshida no Matsue Beauty Daisakusen', 'Yoshida no Matsue Beauty Daisakusen Prologue', '3-bu de Wakaru Koizumi Yakumo no Kaidan', 'Heisei Matsue Kaidan']
